address2: 3rd Floor Jl. Buncit Raya No.139 Kalibata, Pancoran
longBusinessSummary: PT Kokoh Inti Arebama Tbk engages in trading of building materials. It distributes ceramic products, roof tiles, granites, sanitary ware, paints, gypsum, leak-proof coatings, and instant cement products, as well as ceramic floor and wall tiles, and ready-mix and lightweight concrete products. The company offers its products under the KIA, Impresso, Jayamix, and Laurenza brand names. Its marketing and distribution network comprises various branches in Indonesia, including Medan, Pekan Baru, Jambi, Palembang, Bandar Lampung, Jakarta, Bekasi, Bogor, Tangerang, Bandung, Cirebon, Yogyakarta, Semarang, Surabaya, Malang, Denpasar, Banjarmasin, Samarinda, and Makassar. The company was founded in 2001 and is based in Jakarta Selatan, Indonesia. PT Kokoh Inti Arebama Tbk is a subsidiary of SCG Distribution Company Limited.
